    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus, delivering a linear power band and 315 hp. Mated to a crisp 6-speed G96 manual transaxle, the drivetrain provides an engaging, mechanical connection to the road. This example has been properly maintained, including a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recent cooling system overhaul featuring a high-flow water pump. The chassis utilizes an independent multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts, maintaining excellent lateral stability. Braking performance is sharp, thanks to four-piston monoblock calipers and ventilated, cross-drilled rotors. While the finish shows minor signs of use typical of a spirited driver, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptional. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
