      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, showing only minor cosmetic imperfections such as small stone chips on the hood and a light scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, consistent with careful use. Inside, the interior is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system and backup camera, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has benefited from a consistent maintenance schedule, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a cooling system flush. The tires have approximately 75% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It shifts smoothly through all gears and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a dependable, well-documented vehicle ready for many more miles of service.",
